# MoonPad — Anchor Smart Contract Specification

> **Meteora DAMM v2 addendum:** Detailed pool params, account layouts, fee scheduler, TS helpers, and migration notes live in [`meteora`](meteora) (repo root). This file is the authoritative program specification.

## Overview

This document specifies the complete Solana/Anchor program for MoonPad, a Solana memetoken presale launchpad. The program handles presale creation, SOL contributions, early withdrawals, and **Meteora DAMM v2** liquidity when the raise target is met. Liquidity uses **`initialize_customizable_pool`**, then **`permanent_lock_position`** (rug-proof); trading fees (SOL via `collectFeeMode = OnlyB`) are **`claim_fee`**’d into a **`fee_vault` PDA**, then distributed to contributors **pro-rata** via `fee_pool_per_share_x64` / `collect_my_fees`.

**Target raise per presale:** 85 SOL (hardcoded)

**Token split:** 85 SOL + 50% of supply → DAMM v2 pool (locked); 50% of supply stays in `token_vault` for contributor **token** claims.

**Program type:** Single deployed factory program; per-token state stored in PDAs

