**Space calculation:**
```rust
// 8 (discriminator)
// + 32 (mint) + 4+32 (name) + 4+10 (ticker) + 4+200 (uri) + 4+256 (desc)
// + 32 (creator) + 8 + 8 + 8 + 8 (u64s)
// + 8 + 8 + 4 + 8 + 8 (state fields)
// + 1 + 1 + 16 (bool, bool, u128)
// + 1 + 1 + 1 (bumps)
// + 4+100 + 4+100 + 4+100 (socials)
// + max_contribution + DAMM/fee fields + fee_vault_bump — use 1536 for safety
pub const PRESALE_STATE_SIZE: usize = 1536;
```

