## WSOL Handling for DAMM v2

DAMM v2 uses SPL tokens (WSOL + project mint). Wrap **85 SOL** from `vault` into `presale_state`’s WSOL ATA, `sync_native`, then CPI pool init. After Meteora instructions, close the WSOL ATA if empty to reclaim rent (see [`meteora`](meteora) snippet).

